  "purpose" : "(Clinical Focus: This value set includes concepts representing an individual's treatment intervention preferences at end of life which can be expressed by the individual in his or her advance care plan.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this value set is to identify treatment intervention preferences that may be relevant and could be considered by clinicians when making a treatment/care plan for the person with serious illness or at end of life.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include treatment intervention preferences that would be relevant for a person with serious illness or at end of life.),(Exclusion Criteria: )",
